column16: Arismendy Alcantara grounds out, second baseman Jonathan Villar to first baseman Jesus Aguilar.
Jose Peraza lines out to right fielder Domingo Santana.
Scott Schebler walks.   Eugenio Suarez to 2nd.
Eugenio Suarez reaches on a fielder's choice out, shortstop Orlando Arcia to third baseman Travis Shaw to second baseman Jonathan Villar to shortstop Orlando Arcia.   Adam Duvall out at 3rd.
Adam Duvall doubles (22) on a sharp line drive to left fielder Hernan Perez.
Patrick Kivlehan flies out to center fielder Keon Broxton.

Scooter Gennett grounds into a double play, second baseman Jonathan Villar to shortstop Orlando Arcia to first baseman Jesus Aguilar.   Arismendy Alcantara scores.    Stuart Turner to 3rd.    Billy Hamilton out at 2nd.
Billy Hamilton singles on a line drive to left fielder Hernan Perez.   Arismendy Alcantara to 3rd.    Stuart Turner to 2nd.
Stuart Turner singles on a line drive to right fielder Domingo Santana.   Arismendy Alcantara to 2nd.
Umpire reviewed (play at 1st), call on the field was overturned: Arismendy Alcantara singles on a ground ball to second baseman Jonathan Villar.
